org.eclipse.viatra.dse.objectives.impl

Class TrajectoryCostSoftObjective

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.viatra.dse.objectives.impl.BaseObjective
      • org.eclipse.viatra.dse.objectives.impl.TrajectoryCostSoftObjective
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IObjective

    public class TrajectoryCostSoftObjective
extends BaseObjective
    This soft objective calculates a fitness value based on the length of the trajectory. Costs to the rules can be assigned.
    Author:
    Andras Szabolcs Nagy
